SELECT full_name, email, lease_start_date, lease_end_date FROM TenantInformation JOIN LeaseAgreements ON TenantInformation.tenant_id = LeaseAgreements.tenant_id WHERE rent_amount > 1000 ORDER BY lease_end_date DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT tenants.first_name, tenants.last_name, addresses.city FROM tenants JOIN addresses ON tenants.tenant_id = addresses.tenant_id WHERE addresses.state = 'California';

SELECT tenants.first_name, lease_agreements.start_date, payments.amount FROM tenants JOIN lease_agreements ON tenants.tenant_id = lease_agreements.tenant_id JOIN payments ON lease_agreements.agreement_id = payments.agreement_id WHERE lease_agreements.start_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';

SELECT tenants.first_name, notifications.message, notifications.date_sent FROM tenants JOIN notifications ON tenants.tenant_id = notifications.tenant_id WHERE notifications.date_sent > NOW() - INTERVAL 7 DAY;
